dotnet new webapi -n SimpleAPI
cd SimpleAPI
dotnet build 
dotnet new xunit -n SimpleAPI.Test


test and make sure the api runs 
cd src\simpleapi
dotnet run 


cd to test project and and build it after changes 

dotnet test


#let's check this to github
